text: Fernando Zapata (born 15 August 1973) is an Argentine rower. He competed in the men's lightweight double sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Argentina Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
